{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 131869, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么要对牛弹琴？", "timestamp": 1594742171, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 131872, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中美吗", "timestamp": 1594742180, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 131876, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或者说，明知道和这种人讨论不出结果，就没有必要继续讨论了", "timestamp": 1594742213, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 131895, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "补充一条，你在说A不好的时候并不是胡说，是有依据的。但是对面说B不好可能是为了恶心你来说的。", "timestamp": 1594742342, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 131922, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这不就是女拳师嘛，说拳师不好，对方急了说男拳也不好，阴阳怪气说我给男拳洗地", "timestamp": 1594742567, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 131939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 嗯……我提出这个问题确实是基于这个的，但想了想这个问题还可以抽象出来，是普遍存在的", "timestamp": 1594742691, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132005, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "要分情景吧？毕竟选择性只说A好，不说B不好的人也是存在的，还能伪装作理中客的样子好不快活。不过如果是路人上来就开喷实在无语子。", "timestamp": 1594743391, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132009, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "*说A不好", "timestamp": 1594743438, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132017, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: A和B都不一定是一个层面的东西，一般人都很难联想到把这俩放在一起说，这还怎么算选择性呢……", "timestamp": 1594743662, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132051, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 但你说的这个情况也不能说明对面没问题。比如甲说“L倾不好”，乙立马高潮跳出来“你咋不说R倾呢”，这只能说明乙是极L主义，不能说明甲是极R主义。", "timestamp": 1594744043, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 1, "pid": 22685, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "如何看待以下的脑瘫行为：\n当你说A不好的时候，他急了跟你喷B不好；\n实际上你并没有说B好的意思，单纯是要指出A不好。说明这一点的时候，他又阴阳怪气你在给B洗地。", "timestamp": 1594742125, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782591, "url": "", "vote": {}}}